qoriq-rcw (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add --dump mode: read the live RCW snapshot from /dev/mem on a
    running QorIQ/Layerscape board and emit a recompilable .rcw file
    with a header documenting the detected SoC, addresses, and the
    sanity checks performed.
  * New qoriq-rcw-data binary package shipping the canonical .rcwi
    files vendored from nxp-qoriq/rcw.

 -- Vincent Jardin <vjardin@free.fr>  Mon, 13 Apr 2026 14:00:00 +0000

